(158, 1, '2017-05-12 10:27:39', '2017-05-12 10:27:39', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-162\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/kopifolks/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Gudetama-Cafe-Interior.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" />\r\n\r\nvia <a href=\"https://digjapan.travel/en/blog/id=10575\">DIG JAPAN!</a>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-161\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/kopifolks/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Gudetama-Cafe-Dim-Sum.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" />\r\n\r\nvia <a href=\"http://danielfooddiary.com/2015/10/21/gudetamadimsum/\">DanielFoodDiary</a>\r\n\r\nOur favourite <a href=\"https://www.sanrio.com/\">Sanrio</a> egg character is coming to Singapore this November! Many of us can relate to this lazy egg character as it depicts many parts of our lives. <a href=\"https://www.sanrio.com/categories/gudetama\">Gudetama</a> cafe was in the lime-light in Osaka, Japan and a pop-up cafe in Dim Sum paradise, Hong Kong. The super adorable dishes has made it’s way onto our Instagram feed causing us to go “Awwww! I want to try that!” and now we can!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-160\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/kopifolks/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Gudetama-Cafe-Rice.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" />\r\n\r\nvia <a href=\"https://digjapan.travel/en/blog/id=10575\">DIG JAPAN!</a>\r\n\r\nWe don’t know for sure what they’ll be serving, but we can confirm with you that there will be Breakfast in Pan. This includes eggs (most probably in the form of gudetama), toast, bacon and sausages. They will also be serving desserts like waffles, soft serve and coffee.\r\n\r\nSingaporean food blogger, <a href=\"http://littlemissbento.com/\">Little Miss Bento</a> will be in-charge of food styling and co-creating the menu for the Gudetama Cafe. You already know that the dishes are going to be super cute and Instagram-worthy.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-159\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/kopifolks/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Gudetama-Cafe-Singapore.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"951\" />\r\n\r\nvia <a href=\"http://danielfooddiary.com/2016/10/16/gudetamacafesg/\">DanielFoodDiary</a>\r\n\r\nWe can’t wait to visit this Gudetama outlet!\r\n\r\n<strong>Where:</strong> Suntec City Mall #01-361/362/363/364, 3 Temasek Boulevard Singapore 038983', 'How Egg-citing! Gudetama Cafe is Coming to Singapore!', 'Our favourite Sanrio egg character is coming to Singapore this November!', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-egg-citing-gudetama-cafe-is-coming-to-singapore', '', '', '2017-05-16 02:31:05', '2017-05-16 02:31:05', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/kopifolks/?p=158', 0, 'post', '', 0),
